3. Permissions Used by the App

The app requests the following permissions only for functional purposes:

Permission	Purpose
android.permission.INTERNET	To fetch real-time data such as currency or calculation-related info
android.permission.VIBRATE	To provide vibration feedback
android.permission.ACCESS_COARSE_LOCATION	Used only if calculator features require basic location (e.g., regional calculations)
android.permission.ACCESS_FINE_LOCATION	Same as above, only if enabled by the user
android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW	To support floating calculator features
com.google.android.gms.permission.AD_ID	Used by Firebase services (no personalized ads shown)

üîí Location data is NOT stored or shared.

4. Data Security

We value your trust. Since the app does not store personal data, there is no risk of data leakage or misuse from our side.

